window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>One captain’s death might turn out to be humanity’s best chance at survival.</b></p> <p>As humanity expands into the stars, it discovers the universe is a hostile place.</p> <p>When Captain Slater of the USS <i>Franklin </i>is assigned to a deep-space reconnaissance mission, his ship is destroyed by an unknown alien race.</p> <p>Much to his surprise, Slater isn’t killed - he’s transformed. He is now a “derelict” - a consciousness bound to his old vessel.&nbsp;</p> <p>Slater must quickly adapt to his new existence before raiders, alien armies, and mysterious forces seek to destroy him for a second and final time.</p>"; 
